          "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-9705462" , "Provides Input For Rule. The relation 'SOCS1,3:p-4Y-CSF3R:CSF3 dimer:LYN:p-Y-JAK1:p-JAK2:p-SYK:p-HCK:p-TYK2 is endocytosed' 'null' 'SOCS1,3:p-4Y-CSF3R:CSF3 dimer:LYN:p-Y-JAK1:p-JAK2:p-SYK:p-HCK:p-TYK2 binds CUL5, ELOB, ELOC, RNF7' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is an input of reaction 2. " ;
